name: GummiArm
tagline: A compliant and printable robot arm.
body:
![The GummiArm](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mstoelen/GummiArm/master/media/web/gummi_mug_small.jpg)


Welcome to the GummiArm project! 

Checkout the [repository](https://github.com/mstoelen/GummiArm) for the latest code and printables, and the [wiki](https://github.com/mstoelen/GummiArm/wiki) for documentation.

Videos: https://plus.google.com/collection/oGXbV

Part of the DeCoRo project at Plymouth University: http://www.tech.plym.ac.uk/SoCCE/CRNS/decoro/
